---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Sidebar from '../components/Sidebar.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About Eastern Wellness Methods - Our Mission & Team"
  description="Learn about Eastern Wellness Methods, our mission to bring traditional Japanese wellness practices to North America, and meet our team of experts."
  keywords="about us, Eastern Wellness Methods, Japanese wellness experts, traditional Japanese medicine, wellness mission"
  canonicalUrl="https://yourdomain.com/about"
  author="Eastern Wellness Methods"
>
  <main class="flex-1 w-full max-w-6xl mx-auto pb-12 px-6">
    <section class="pt-10 pb-8 max-w-4xl">
      <span class="inline-block py-1.5 px-3 rounded-full bg-emerald-100 dark:bg-emerald-900/30 text-accent-dark dark:text-emerald-400 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider mb-4 border border-emerald-200 dark:border-emerald-800">About Us</span>
      <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold leading-tight text-text-main-light dark:text-text-main-dark mb-6">
        Bringing Ancient Wisdom to Modern Wellness
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-text-muted-light dark:text-text-muted-dark">
        Discover how Eastern Wellness Methods is bridging traditional Japanese wellness practices with contemporary health needs.
      </p>
    </section>

    <div class="lg:grid lg:grid-cols-12 lg:gap-12">
      <article class="lg:col-span-8 space-y-8">

        <!-- Hero Image -->
        <figure class="mb-8">
          <div class="w-full aspect-[16/9] bg-gray-200 dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg relative">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-cover bg-center transition-transform hover:scale-105 duration-1000" style="background-image: url('https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuDpIXyBn9Z6-Rpv2U84It-v3XCsL8X7w4AbFZFgIsljYH2MDTrEpoq5MW1TBySesaDdt1nrHIoEDyoahvG7pjG9z6nIuKtgS7hKM51Pa9D9br0wyRf8vskBbu_ajoGi9EKPKjtRoQo4bRe65NOPICZH7Xs3bu51kGZL5t4QBg9OhBhzAIlq8uzQlDhxqW1N3v2_XT0P34YblkelpNVq89IqsVH89fl7AtPjvG2JwG9mUibT4U3dibr4M71L2k4NJr50IeNxtVsPEe4H');">
            </div>
          </div>
          <figcaption class="text-sm text-text-muted-light dark:text-text-muted-dark mt-3 italic text-center">
            Our mission is to make traditional Japanese wellness accessible to everyone.
          </figcaption>
        </figure>

        <!-- Our Story -->
        <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold text-accent-dark dark:text-emerald-400 pt-4" id="our-story">
          My Story
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl leading-relaxed text-text-main-light dark:text-gray-300 font-normal">
          <span class="text-6xl float-left font-serif font-bold text-accent-dark dark:text-emerald-400 mr-4 mt-[-8px] leading-none">L</span>ike many people over 50, I found myself struggling with chronic back and neck pain. As a developer spending countless hours at a desk, the pain had become my constant companion. Traditional treatments provided only temporary relief, and I knew there had to be a better way.
        </p>
        <p class="text-xl leading-relaxed text-text-main-light dark:text-gray-300 font-normal">
          That's when I discovered traditional Japanese wellness practices. Simple techniques like the towel stretches developed by practitioners like Dr. Toshiki Fukutsudzi and other Japanese physical therapy methods changed my life. These gentle, consistent movements didn't just mask the pain—they addressed the root causes.
        </p>
        <p class="text-xl leading-relaxed text-text-main-light dark:text-gray-300 font-normal">
          Eastern Wellness Methods was born from this personal transformation. I'm not a medical professional—I'm someone who found real relief through these time-tested techniques and wants to share them with others who are suffering like I was. Everything I share is based on established Japanese wellness practices, backed by research, and properly attributed to the experts who developed these methods.
        </p>

        <!-- Our Mission -->
        <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold text-accent-dark dark:text-emerald-400 pt-4" id="our-mission">
          My Mission
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl leading-relaxed text-text-main-light dark:text-gray-300 font-normal">
          I believe that wellness shouldn't be complicated or expensive. My mission is to share the traditional Japanese wellness practices that helped me, making them accessible and understandable for others facing similar challenges. Through carefully researched content that properly credits the experts and practitioners who developed these techniques, I aim to help people:
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-4 my-6">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <span class="flex-shrink-0 size-6 rounded-full bg-accent-dark text-white flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold mt-1">✓</span>
            <span class="text-xl text-text-main-light dark:text-gray-300">Relieve chronic pain through gentle, sustainable practices</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <span class="flex-shrink-0 size-6 rounded-full bg-accent-dark text-white flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold mt-1">✓</span>
            <span class="text-xl text-text-main-light dark:text-gray-300">Improve flexibility and mobility at any age</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <span class="flex-shrink-0 size-6 rounded-full bg-accent-dark text-white flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold mt-1">✓</span>
            <span class="text-xl text-text-main-light dark:text-gray-300">Build sustainable wellness habits rooted in centuries of wisdom</span>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <span class="flex-shrink-0 size-6 rounded-full bg-accent-dark text-white flex items-center justify-center text-sm font-bold mt-1">✓</span>
            <span class="text-xl text-text-main-light dark:text-gray-300">Prevent future health issues through preventative care</span>
          </li>
        </ul>

        <!-- Our Approach -->
        <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold text-accent-dark dark:text-emerald-400 pt-4" id="our-approach">
          Our Approach
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl leading-relaxed text-text-main-light dark:text-gray-300 font-normal">
          What sets Eastern Wellness Methods apart is our commitment to authenticity combined with scientific validation. Every technique we share is:
        </p>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-8">
          <div class="bg-white dark:bg-surface-dark p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 shadow-sm">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-accent-dark dark:text-emerald-400 text-3xl">verified</span>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-text-main-light dark:text-text-main-dark">Traditionally Rooted</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-base text-text-muted-light dark:text-text-muted-dark">Based on authentic Japanese wellness practices passed down through generations of practitioners.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white dark:bg-surface-dark p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 shadow-sm">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-accent-dark dark:text-emerald-400 text-3xl">science</span>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-text-main-light dark:text-text-main-dark">Evidence-Based</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-base text-text-muted-light dark:text-text-muted-dark">Supported by modern research and validated through clinical studies and peer-reviewed literature.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white dark:bg-surface-dark p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 shadow-sm">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-accent-dark dark:text-emerald-400 text-3xl">accessibility</span>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-text-main-light dark:text-text-main-dark">Accessible</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-base text-text-muted-light dark:text-text-muted-dark">Designed for people of all fitness levels and ages, requiring minimal or no equipment.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white dark:bg-surface-dark p-6 rounded-xl border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 shadow-sm">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-3">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-accent-dark dark:text-emerald-400 text-3xl">clear_day</span>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-text-main-light dark:text-text-main-dark">Practical</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-base text-text-muted-light dark:text-text-muted-dark">Easy to integrate into daily routines with clear, step-by-step instructions you can follow.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- About Me -->
        <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold text-accent-dark dark:text-emerald-400 pt-4" id="about-me">
          About Me
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl leading-relaxed text-text-main-light dark:text-gray-300 font-normal mb-8">
          I'm a developer in my 50s who discovered the power of traditional Japanese wellness practices through personal necessity. After years of struggling with back pain, these gentle techniques gave me my life back.
        </p>

        <!-- Personal Bio Card -->
        <div class="bg-white dark:bg-surface-dark rounded-xl p-8 shadow-lg border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 mb-6">
          <div class="flex-1">
            <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-text-main-light dark:text-text-main-dark mb-2">Who I Am</h3>
            <p class="text-sm font-bold text-accent-dark dark:text-emerald-400 uppercase tracking-wide mb-3">Developer & Wellness Advocate</p>
            <p class="text-base text-text-muted-light dark:text-text-muted-dark leading-relaxed mb-4">
              I'm not a doctor or certified physical therapist. I'm a regular person who spent years battling chronic back and neck pain from desk work. When I discovered Japanese wellness practices in my 50s, everything changed.
            </p>
            <p class="text-base text-text-muted-light dark:text-text-muted-dark leading-relaxed mb-4">
              This site shares the techniques that worked for me, always with proper attribution to the Japanese practitioners and researchers who developed them—like Dr. Toshiki Fukutsudzi's towel method, and the traditional practices of Sotai and Makko-Ho.
            </p>
            <p class="text-base text-text-muted-light dark:text-text-muted-dark leading-relaxed">
              <strong class="text-text-main-light dark:text-text-main-dark">Important:</strong> I share these practices based on my personal experience and research, but I always recommend consulting with qualified healthcare professionals before starting any new exercise routine, especially if you have existing health conditions.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- My Values -->
        <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold text-accent-dark dark:text-emerald-400 pt-4" id="my-values">
          My Principles
        </h2>
        <div class="space-y-6 my-8">
          <div class="border-l-4 border-accent-dark pl-6 py-2">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-xl text-text-main-light dark:text-text-main-dark mb-2">Honesty</h3>
            <p class="text-base text-text-muted-light dark:text-text-muted-dark">I share what worked for me personally, always with proper attribution to the experts who developed these techniques.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="border-l-4 border-accent-dark pl-6 py-2">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-xl text-text-main-light dark:text-text-main-dark mb-2">Transparency</h3>
            <p class="text-base text-text-muted-light dark:text-text-muted-dark">I'm clear about my limitations—I'm not a medical professional, just someone sharing their journey and research.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="border-l-4 border-accent-dark pl-6 py-2">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-xl text-text-main-light dark:text-text-main-dark mb-2">Research-Based</h3>
            <p class="text-base text-text-muted-light dark:text-text-muted-dark">Every technique I share comes from established Japanese practices with proper citations and references.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="border-l-4 border-accent-dark pl-6 py-2">
            <h3 class="font-bold text-xl text-text-main-light dark:text-text-main-dark mb-2">Safety First</h3>
            <p class="text-base text-text-muted-light dark:text-text-muted-dark">I always recommend consulting healthcare professionals and never claim to replace medical advice.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- What You Can Expect -->
        <h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold text-accent-dark dark:text-emerald-400 pt-4" id="what-to-expect">
          What You Can Expect From This Site
        </h2>
        <p class="text-xl leading-relaxed text-text-main-light dark:text-gray-300 font-normal">
          I'm committed to providing honest, well-researched information about traditional Japanese wellness practices. Here's what you'll find:
        </p>
        <ul class="space-y-3 my-6 ml-6">
          <li class="text-lg text-text-main-light dark:text-gray-300">✦ Personal experiences with Japanese wellness techniques that helped my chronic pain</li>
          <li class="text-lg text-text-main-light dark:text-gray-300">✦ Properly attributed information from established Japanese practitioners and researchers</li>
          <li class="text-lg text-text-main-light dark:text-gray-300">✦ References to peer-reviewed research supporting these traditional practices</li>
          <li class="text-lg text-text-main-light dark:text-gray-300">✦ Clear disclaimers that this is educational content, not medical advice</li>
          <li class="text-lg text-text-main-light dark:text-gray-300">✦ Honest acknowledgment that I'm a regular person sharing what worked for me</li>
          <li class="text-lg text-text-main-light dark:text-gray-300">✦ Recommendations to consult qualified healthcare professionals for medical concerns</li>
        </ul>

        <!-- Disclaimer -->
        <div class="bg-amber-50 dark:bg-amber-900/20 rounded-2xl p-8 mt-8 border border-amber-200 dark:border-amber-800">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-amber-600 dark:text-amber-400 text-3xl flex-shrink-0">warning</span>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-bold text-xl text-text-main-light dark:text-text-main-dark mb-3">Medical Disclaimer</h3>
              <p class="text-base text-text-muted-light dark:text-text-muted-dark leading-relaxed mb-3">
                The information on this website is for educational purposes only and based on my personal experience with traditional Japanese wellness practices. I am not a licensed medical professional, physical therapist, or healthcare provider.
              </p>
              <p class="text-base text-text-muted-light dark:text-text-muted-dark leading-relaxed">
                <strong>Always consult with qualified healthcare professionals before starting any new exercise or wellness routine, especially if you have pre-existing medical conditions, chronic pain, or injuries.</strong> The techniques shared here are based on established Japanese practices and research, but individual results may vary.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Call to Action -->
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-50 to-teal-50 dark:from-emerald-900/20 dark:to-teal-900/20 rounded-2xl p-8 mt-12 border border-emerald-200 dark:border-emerald-800">
          <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl font-bold text-accent-dark dark:text-emerald-400 mb-4">Explore Japanese Wellness Practices</h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-text-main-light dark:text-gray-300 mb-6">
            Discover the traditional techniques that helped me overcome chronic back pain and improve my quality of life.
          </p>
          <a href="/" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-accent-dark hover:bg-emerald-800 text-white font-bold py-3 px-6 rounded-lg transition-colors shadow-md hover:shadow-lg">
            Read My Articles
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">arrow_forward</span>
          </a>
        </div>

      </article>

      <Sidebar tocItems={[
        { href: "#our-story", text: "Our Story" },
        { href: "#our-mission", text: "Our Mission" },
        { href: "#our-approach", text: "Our Approach" },
        { href: "#about-me", text: "About Me" },
        { href: "#my-values", text: "My Values" },
        { href: "#what-to-expect", text: "What to Expect" },
      ]} />
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
